Which component of the study is considered experimental for the caregivers participating in the research?
A) Completing surveys sent via email or over the phone at 1, 3, and 6 months;
B) Using the Cope 360 app for symptom tracking, medication management, and emergency preparedness;
C) Receiving standard education about caregiving for children with cancer;
D) Receiving gift cards for completing various stages of the study.

Correct answer: B
